  <Summary>The most anticipated issue of this arc is finally here. Needless to say this issue focuses on Larry and Rita's walk from 5th through the tunnel but Martins and Perkins together paint an amazing city backdrop for every frame and the writing is as always top notch. A brilliant issue which explores Larry's character adding depth to the once famous pop star.

Stu Redman is also on a journey in this issue and stumbles across a most welcome surprise.</Summary>
